    <surveyls_email_invite_subj><![CDATA[Invitation to participate in a survey]]></surveyls_email_invite_subj>
    <surveyls_email_invite><![CDATA[Dear {FIRSTNAME},<br />
<br />
You have been invited to participate in a survey.<br />
<br />
The survey is titled:<br />
"{SURVEYNAME}"<br />
<br />
"{SURVEYDESCRIPTION}"<br />
<br />
To participate, please click on the link below.<br />
<br />
Sincerely,<br />
<br />
{ADMINNAME} ({ADMINEMAIL})<br />
<br />
----------------------------------------------<br />
Click here to do the survey:<br />
{SURVEYURL}<br />
<br />
If you do not want to participate in this survey and don't want to receive any more invitations please click the following link:<br />
{OPTOUTURL}<br />
<br />
If you are blocklisted but want to participate in this survey and want to receive invitations please click the following link:<br />
{OPTINURL}]]></surveyls_email_invite>
    <surveyls_email_remind_subj><![CDATA[Reminder to participate in a survey]]></surveyls_email_remind_subj>
    <surveyls_email_remind><![CDATA[Dear {FIRSTNAME},<br />
<br />
Recently we invited you to participate in a survey.<br />
<br />
We note that you have not yet completed the survey, and wish to remind you that the survey is still available should you wish to take part.<br />
<br />
The survey is titled:<br />
"{SURVEYNAME}"<br />
<br />
"{SURVEYDESCRIPTION}"<br />
<br />
To participate, please click on the link below.<br />
<br />
Sincerely,<br />
<br />
{ADMINNAME} ({ADMINEMAIL})<br />
<br />
----------------------------------------------<br />
Click here to do the survey:<br />
{SURVEYURL}<br />
<br />
If you do not want to participate in this survey and don't want to receive any more invitations please click the following link:<br />
{OPTOUTURL}]]></surveyls_email_remind>
    <surveyls_email_register_subj><![CDATA[Survey registration confirmation]]></surveyls_email_register_subj>
    <surveyls_email_register><![CDATA[Dear {FIRSTNAME},<br />
<br />
You, or someone using your email address, have registered to participate in an online survey titled {SURVEYNAME}.<br />
<br />
To complete this survey, click on the following URL:<br />
<br />
{SURVEYURL}<br />
<br />
If you have any questions about this survey, or if you did not register to participate and believe this email is in error, please contact {ADMINNAME} at {ADMINEMAIL}.]]></surveyls_email_register>
    <surveyls_email_confirm_subj><![CDATA[Confirmation of your participation in our survey]]></surveyls_email_confirm_subj>
    <surveyls_email_confirm><![CDATA[Dear {FIRSTNAME},<br />
<br />
This email is to confirm that you have completed the survey titled {SURVEYNAME} and your response has been saved. Thank you for participating.<br />
<br />
If you have any further questions about this email, please contact {ADMINNAME} on {ADMINEMAIL}.<br />
<br />
Sincerely,<br />
<br />
{ADMINNAME}]]></surveyls_email_confirm>
    <surveyls_dateformat><![CDATA[9]]></surveyls_dateformat>
    <surveyls_alias/>
    <email_admin_notification_subj><![CDATA[Response submission for survey {SURVEYNAME}]]></email_admin_notification_subj>
    <email_admin_notification><![CDATA[Hello,<br />
<br />
A new response was submitted for your survey '{SURVEYNAME}'.<br />
<br />
Click the following link to see the individual response:<br />
{VIEWRESPONSEURL}<br />
<br />
Click the following link to edit the individual response:<br />
{EDITRESPONSEURL}<br />
<br />
View statistics by clicking here:<br />
{STATISTICSURL}]]></email_admin_notification>
    <email_admin_responses_subj><![CDATA[Response submission for survey {SURVEYNAME} with results]]></email_admin_responses_subj>
    <email_admin_responses><![CDATA[Hello,<br />
<br />
A new response was submitted for your survey '{SURVEYNAME}'.<br />
<br />
Click the following link to see the individual response:<br />
{VIEWRESPONSEURL}<br />
<br />
Click the following link to edit the individual response:<br />
{EDITRESPONSEURL}<br />
<br />
View statistics by clicking here:<br />
{STATISTICSURL}<br />
<br />
<br />
The following answers were given by the participant:<br />
{ANSWERTABLE}]]></email_admin_responses>
    <surveyls_numberformat><![CDATA[0]]></surveyls_numberformat>
    <surveyls_language><![CDATA[en]]></surveyls_language>
    <surveyls_title><![CDATA[Impact of Linguistic Styles on Trust in Educational Chatbots]]></surveyls_title>
    <surveyls_description/>
    <surveyls_welcometext><![CDATA[<p data-path-to-node="7,0">Welcome to this study on the effects of gender-aware language on educational chatbots.</p>

<p data-path-to-node="7,0">This study explores how different language styles of a mentoring chatbot in Computer Science affect user trust, enjoyment, and perceived usefulness. The findings will support a Bachelor's thesis investigating the effects of gender-aware language in chatbot interactions.</p>

<p data-path-to-node="7,0">This survey is conducted by Ahju Jang, a Computer Science student at the Technical University of Darmstadt. If you have any questions, please contact me at ahju.jang@stud.tu-darmstadt.de.</p>

<p>The survey will take approximately 15 to 20 minutes to complete. Your participation is voluntary, and you may stop the survey at any time. We collect some general demographic information to help us analyze our results; however, all entries are optional.</p>

<p>Please note that the chat conversations will be stored and analyzed as part of this study. During the chat, you have the option to provide a name. This does not have to be your real name; a nickname is perfectly sufficient and will only be used for a more personalized interaction with the bot. Please do not share any personally identifiable information during the chatbot interaction.</p>

<p><strong>By clicking 'Next', you confirm that you are at least 18 years of age, have read the information above, and voluntarily agree to participate in this study.</strong></p>

<p>Thank you very much for your contribution!</p>
]]></surveyls_welcometext>
    <surveyls_endtext><![CDATA[<p><strong>Thank you for participating in this study! </strong>Your response is highly appreciated.</p>

<p>If you have any remaining questions, please feel free to contact me at ahju.jang@stud.tu-darmstadt.de.</p>

<p> </p>

<p>You may now close this window.</p>

<p> </p>

<p>Redeem Survey Code with one click: <a href="https://www.surveycircle.com/ZT28-LXYK-DSJY-P5J7/" target="_blank">https://www.surveycircle.com/ZT28-LXYK-DSJY-P5J7/</a></p>
]]></surveyls_endtext>
    <surveyls_policy_notice><![CDATA[Your data will be treated confidentially and processed pseudonymously. It will not be shared with third parties and will be deleted once the analysis is complete.]]></surveyls_policy_notice>
